We want our people to be committed to data

protection and regular training Siemens’ employees receive regular training on how to

handle personal data that is tailored to specific functions and target groups. For this purpose, we developed a web- based data protection training program consisting of an “Essentials” level that is mandatory for all employees who process personal data as part of their job and specialized “Nuggets” designed for specific fields and target groups.

Data privacy management system to ensure compliance with data protection requirements in all business processes